metadata.name: Abandon Normal Instruments
metadata.description:
"They all go into the dark, the vacant interstellar spaces," T.S. Eliot

This piece represents the essence, or a distillation of my visual language. It also symbolises me and my journey as an artist in the digital space, and where I might be headed next. 

This open edition holds possibilities for projects and collaborations in the future, but for now, I hope you collect the piece because you like the art or wish to show support.
